            crucial role for the project&rsquo;s experiment planning and
            execution. Lastly, he was in constant contact with team&rsquo;s
            supervisors to inform them about the project&rsquo;s progress and
            get both feedback and advice from them to smoothly proceed in the
            project&rsquo;s completion.
          </p>
