            set would be met. She played a significant role in the process of
            organizing educational activities in order to create a bridge
            between the concept of synthetic biology and the different social
            groups.Additionally, she contributed in the collaboration&nbsp; with
            other teams and the participation in activities held by IGEM
            Community in order for the team to be actively present.
          </p>
